<item>
            <title>[GROOVY-1308] MarkupBuilder replaces &apos; characters with the incorrect entity &amp;quot;</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-1308</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When MarkupBuilder escapes both attribute values and element content, it replaces the &apos; character with the entity &amp;quot;, rather than &amp;apos;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12813061">GROOVY-1308</key>
            <summary>MarkupBuilder replaces &apos; characters with the incorrect entity &amp;quot;</summary>
